Info:
~~~~~
Back again with a Liverecording from my
DJ-set at the Main01 Festival in Marseille.
Recorded from the output of the mixer, and
edited afterwards to suite the purpose of
being the Second volume of Piratesessions
wich means I removed the material from Ps1
that I played on the party. Enjoy!

Featured Artists:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
(In order of Apperance).
Zabutom, Tempest, Reed, Mr Death, 4mat,
Kraftwerk, Loonie, Goto 80 and PurpleMotion.
